## Quick Reference
- 2xx: Success responses
- 3xx: Redirects
- 4xx: Client mistakes
- 5xx: Server problems

## Common API Usage
- GET success: 200
- POST success: 201
- PUT/PATCH success: 200 or 204
- DELETE success: 200 or 204
- Validation errors: 400 or 422
- Auth errors: 401 or 403
- Not found: 404
- Server crashes: 500
